'''Khosana Ilia Chavchavadze''' (Segeorgia: ილია ჭავჭავაძე; 8 Pulungoana 1837 - 12 Loetse 1907) e ne e le motho oa sechaba oa Georgia, moqolotsi oa litaba, mohatisi, mongoli le seroki ea nkileng karolo e kholo ho thehoeng ha mekhatlo ea sechaba ea Georgia nakong ea puso ea Russia ea Georgia. O bitsoa "mohale ea hlomphuoang ka ho fetisisa lefatšeng ka bophara" oa Georgia.

E ne e le moetapele oa mokhatlo oa bocha ba mahlale o bitsoang "Tergdaleulebi". Ilia Chavchavadze o thehile likoranta tse 2 tsa sejoale-joale: Sakartvelos Moambe le Iveria. O phethile karolo ea bohlokoa ho theheng sebopeho sa pele sa lichelete Georgia - Land Bank of Tbilisi. Nakong ea lilemo tse 30 e ne e le molulasetulo oa Banka ena, e neng e tšehetsa le ho ntšetsa pele liketsahalo tse ngata tsa setso, thuto, moruo le liphallelo tse etsahetseng Georgia. Ilia Chavchavadze o nkile karolo ho theho ea "Society for the Spreading of Literacy among Georgia" - e ne e le mokhatlo oa pele oa mofuta oa NGO o ileng oa theha likolo ho potoloha Georgia, ba leka ho etsa puo ea Segeorgia naheng. Ba ithutile ho ngolla le ho bala batho. Eo e ne e le tsela ea ho loants'a leano la Russification la Mmuso oa Russia o Georgia. O ile a bolaoa ka 1907.
